data.description: PACK YOUR BAGS, your search is over. This 4 bedroom home has been renovated to the studs and transformed to cozy buyer's dream home. All the work has been in this turnkey property located in Southwest Fort Worth. All new hardwood flooring flows throughout the home, white Quartz kitchen and bathroom counters, new cabinetry, hardware, classic subway tile and other designer touches. Load s of natural light shines through the new windows and recessed lighting has been installed in the ceiling, as well as fans. The roof, HVAC, electrical, water heater and foundation, it's all been done. The yard has a new fence and covered patio great for entertaining. This gem is ready for new owners. Call for details.
